<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.1">
<l>puḷḷuru vāki naḷḷiruḷ vanta pūtaṉai māḷavi laṅkai</l>
<l>yoḷḷeri maṇṭi yuṇṇa<supplied>p</supplied>pa ṇitta vūkkama taṉaini ṉaintō,</l>
<l>kaḷḷaviḻ kōtai kātalu meṅkaḷ kārikai mātarka ruttum,</l>
<l>piḷḷaitaṉ kaiyil kiṇṇamē yokkap pēcuva tentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Were you] remembering the power conferred to kill Pūtanā</l>
<l rend="indent">who came at midnight as a bird,</l>
<l>Or to consume Laṅkā, attacking it with blazing fire, my father, lord,</l>
<l>That your speaking of the love by our [girl] with a nectar-dripping chaplet,</l>
<l>Or of those women’s opinions of our beautiful girl,</l>
<l rend="indent">was like [stealing] a cup in a baby’s hand?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
